Text: I just compared it with the recent upload http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5117120/Karajan_Conducts_Tchaikovsky___(8_CD_Box_Set) : the first three symphonies seem to be the same recordings, the last three are a decade later (76 vs 64-66) in the present set. So, if you already have the above-mentioned set, you can dowload CD3 and CD4 from this one to 'have something new'.
